{"tid":819987,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「啤牌同好入」Monarchs君王","createTime":"2018-09-15T07:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T07:38:18.000Z","uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e18852ccc98e89f4f2030ffba47383b233f2f9c","tid":819987,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"喺三年前，小弟我第一次接觸魔術就係喺一個商場既魔術推廣event。<br />\n仲記得當時有個外國魔術師做啤牌魔術既表演，喺魔術師華麗既手法之外，整個表演最吸引我既就係魔術師手上既一副啤牌。<br />\n<br />\n聽現場工作人員介紹，呢副啤牌叫「Monarchs」，中文意思即係「君王」，喺由美國一間好出名既魔術公司設計，再由USPCC（US Playing card company）印製。<br />\n<br />\n呢副啤牌既設計理念係希望切合「君王」既感覺，創造一副皇族專用，尊貴典雅而不至浮誇囂狂既啤牌。<br />\n<br />\n首先喺牌盒上面可以見到大量用金色油墨壓印既金色線條，感覺極度搶眼，而且有凹凸設計，手感過癮。加上牌盒所採用既紙質優良，厚實而不笨重。單單喺牌盒拎上手已經好有潮流品味既感覺。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/151835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F151835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=41436b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/151837_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F151837_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4a1d4c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/151839_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F151839_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a87b999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來嚟就係啤牌本身，牌背豐富既設計亦一樣吸引，例如劍，葉，蛇交錯既設計，背後仿似蘊藏左一個個未知既故事。邊線上面既紋路同埋字句更加係做到最成功既點綴。<br />\n<br />\n每副啤牌既靈魂 - 黑桃Ace ，亦有皇冠既設計，而且有用到金屬油墨既技術，再一次完美切合「君王」既主題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/152849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F152849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d5b16337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/152852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F152852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bab9cc77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢副啤牌深深咁吸引左我，直到兩年前我正式開始玩魔術，我終於都買左呢副牌。<br />\n某程度上呢副牌可以算係我玩魔術/啤牌收藏既契機。<br />\n<br />\n利申：Monarchs 有幾隻色，例如藍紅綠，仲有更貴既黑金白金黑銀白銀。而我只係買左綠色，因為當初睇到個魔術師用既就係綠色。<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴大睇我分享下我既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7332d2d6a634c35479fbaf435c6e1e83d6d8ed77","tid":819987,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/153806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F153806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce612786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/153809_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F153809_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=16ec422e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/153811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F153811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9aad5acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/153813_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F153813_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=91f37dcf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}